snippet.title: Emperor: Battle for Dune - Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a trailer for the last Dune game: Emperor - Battle for Dune. The Dune RTS-games came first in 1992 with westwood studios Dune 2. 
The Dune Sci-Fi-Books where written by the brilliant Frank Herbert.
This is downloaded for free at: ftp://ftp.westwood.com/
